race.comment: EXTREME DIAMOND (4) will be rock-hard fit for this and maps ideally for this contest from gate two. Gets some weight relief with the 1.5kg claim and must be respected out of the Maher camp. Best figures measure up nicely. DAVIKAR (11) returned in fine fashion with a solid Gold Coast victory and winning rider Youngberry retains the mount. Gets in well at the weights with her 3kg claim and should be going very close again. BLUE ALLURE (10) has been thereabouts in recent efforts and is sure to get a soft run from the inside marble. Top-three prospects. SIMPLY EXCELS (3) has only missed a drum once in six attempts over this six-furlong journey and has to be included in calculations. BOTANICA (1) strips fitter third-up from the break and may earn a cheque.
